		<h3>Formats:</h3>
		<p>xml</p>
		<h3>HTTP Method:</h3>
		<p>GET</p>
		<h3>Requires Authentication:</h3>

		<p>false</p>
		<h3>Parameters:</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<b>comment_id.</b> Required. Article comment will be retrieved by comment_id .
				<br />
