		<h2>New article comment</h1>
		<p>Add new comment to an article</p>
		<h3>URL:</h3>
		<p><%= @presenter.home %>/api/article_comment.format</p>
		<h3>Formats:</h3>
		<p>xml</p>
		<h3>HTTP Method:</h3>
		<p>POST</p>
		<h3>Requires Authentication:</h3>

		<p>false</p>
		<h3>Parameters:</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<b>article_id.</b> Required. The article that the comment will be added.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>title.</b> Required. The title of the comment.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>name.</b> Optional. The name of the author.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>email.</b> Optional. The email of the author.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>body.</b> Optional. The body of the comment.
			</li>
			<li>
				<b>is_valid.</b> Optional. If value = 1 than skip validation (For testing. It will be removed on production!).
			</li>
		</ul> 
	</body>
